The global N-Butanol market is expected to witness significant growth in the forecast period due to the increasing demand for N-Butanol in various end-use industries such as automotive, paints and coatings, and chemical manufacturing. N-Butanol is widely used as a solvent in these industries, driving the market growth. The growth of the automotive sector, coupled with the rise in construction activities worldwide, is further fueling the demand for N-Butanol. Additionally, the shift towards eco-friendly products and the increasing adoption of bio-based N-Butanol are expected to create lucrative opportunities for market growth.

